domain.locations

Class GameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • domain.locations.GameObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DamageRepair, LaserControl, NetControl, OxygenControl, ScanningControl, SteeringControl

    public abstract class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object
    An object within the game that is interact-able. Either by directly using it, or picking it up for later use. An example could be a chair or an air tank. Different kinds of GameObjects can be found here: GameObjectType
    See Also:
    GameObjectType, Interact
